CONTINUITY: When Wonder Woman, Princess of Themyscira is KO'd, for the rest of the game opposing characters modify attack +1 when attacking only characters with the Amazon keyword.
CHAMPION OF THEMYSCIRA: SWORD OF ATHENA: Wonder Woman, Princess of Themyscira may start the game with any Wonder Woman Equipment equipped. // If Wonder Woman, Princess of Themyscira is equipped with WW80 #s004 Sword of Athena, her critical hits deal penetrating damage.
(+1) LEAD THE AMAZON WARRIORS INTO BATTLE: FREE: Choose a friendly character with the Amazon keyword. This turn, that character modifies attack +1.
(-1) DEFENDING THEMYSCIRA FROM THE OUTSIDE WORLD: FREE: Generate a WW80 #004 Amazon Warrior on click #1. Until your next turn, when Wonder Woman, Princess of Themyscira evades an attack, after resolutions choose one: gain 1 Plot Point -or- deal the attacker 1 penetrating damage.
(-5) PROTECT MAN'S WORLD FROM THE ENEMIES OF THEMYSCIRA: FREE: Turn Wonder Woman, Princess of Themyscira to click #11. This game she has Cosmic Energy team ability, SAFEGUARD: Pulse Wave, and can't be damaged. // At the beginning of your turn, if there are no other friendly characters with the Amazon keyword on the map, you lose the game.
